New for the Championships 2014.
A fully redesigned visually rich experience that can be personalised allowing the fan to control the type of information they want to see for the players, event or country of their choice, and also share all content across a variety of social media platforms.

The app contains updated scores, draws, statistics and player information for The Championships 2016.
Also contains enhanced push messaging and favourites, increased video content and other improvements.
Finally, a new experience for visitors to The Championships - Plan Your Visit, and, for all Wimbledon fans - create and share your Wimbledon Story.
